Inside the gym, attendees utilize tablets at kiosks to upload their resumes to the fair database, contributing to the atmosphere that buzzes with anticipation. Workshops on networking etiquette are scheduled to begin in the adjoining classroom, enhancing the experience. A data science company showcases a live dashboard of fair attendance, while healthcare providers display photos from their community outreach efforts, adding to the engagement of the event. Near the exit, a post-event survey link flashes on monitors, providing a way for attendees to give feedback after the event. The dean visits to thank recruiters for their support of the university.
